author: mgrigorov
msg: Add a check for 'null' when iterating over the non-submitted tasks.
A task may be submitted during the iteration and in this case ThreadPoolExecutor#getQueue().iretator().next() may return null.

author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3887 Problems concerning IE9 with "ActiveX Filtering" enabled
Feature detection improvement - first try availability of window.DOMParser and then fallback to window.ActiveXObject.
This way IE9 works as the other browsers.
